snippet.title: NFL Sports Talk Football '93 Starring Joe Montana Sega Genesis Gameplay HD
snippet.description:
NFL Sports Talk Football '93 Starring Joe Montana Sega Genesis Gameplay HD. A match between Detroit Lions and Arizona Cardinals.

NFL Sports Talk Football '93 is an American football video game featuring Joe Montana, released in 1992. It is the third in the series, and the first to be licensed by the National Football League.
